    <div class="single-header__title text-center text-sm-left">
      <h1>Un nou site de informare, la nivelul europenilor</h1>
            <div class="d-bloc my-2 publish_date_time">Publicat pe 26 mai 2020 la 05:34</div>    </div>
    <div class="single-header__author">
      <ul>
                  <li><a href="https://voxeurop.eu/ro/author/redactionve/" title="Posts by Voxeurop editorial board" class="author url fn" rel="author">Voxeurop editorial board</a>                      </li>
                          <li>Translated by <a
              href="https://voxeurop.eu/ro/author/aspanu/">Alexandra Spanu</a>
          </li>
                      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="single-article__language single-article__language__mobile">
      <ul> <li><a class='ro wpml-ls-link'  href='javascript:void(0)'>ro </a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link fr" href="https://voxeurop.eu/fr/un-nouveau-site-pour-informer-a-hauteur-deuropeens/">fr</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link en" href="https://voxeurop.eu/en/a-new-website-for-informing-on-a-european-scale/">en</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link cs" href="https://voxeurop.eu/cs/novy-web-na-evropske-urovni/">cs</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link nl" href="https://voxeurop.eu/nl/een-nieuwe-website-om-de-lezers-op-europees-niveau-te-informeren/">nl</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link de" href="https://voxeurop.eu/de/eine-neue-website-um-sie-auf-europaeischem-niveau-zu-informieren/">de</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link it" href="https://voxeurop.eu/it/un-nuovo-sito-per-informarsi-ad-altezza-europea/">it</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link pt-pt" href="https://voxeurop.eu/pt-pt/um-novo-site-para-informar-a-nivel-europeu/">pt-pt</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link es" href="https://voxeurop.eu/es/una-nueva-pagina-web-para-informar-a-nivel-europeo/">es</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link pl" href="https://voxeurop.eu/pl/nowa-strona-informujaca-wszystkich-europejczykow/">pl</a></li></ul>      <div class="mobile-language-separator"></div>
